      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，这是核心控制区。需要五个组件：Canonicalizer做规范化，Detectors做检测，Policy Engine决策，Tool Gate控制工具调用，还有Response Validator校验返回。",
